# Navigation Component

Navigation elements (navbars, menus, tabs, pills) help users move through your site or application.

## Usage

```html
<ul class="nav">
  <li class="nav-item">
    <a class="nav-link active" href="#">Home</a>
  </li>
  <li class="nav-item">
    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Features</a>
  </li>
  <li class="nav-item">
    <a class="nav-link" href="#">Pricing</a>
  </li>
</ul>
```

